snippet.title: [HELP PURPLE] Game App for iPhone & iPad
snippet.description:
■ 'PURPLE'  HomePage :  http://global.helppurple.com

Hello my name is Purple! 
People call me 'Purple', because my skin is purple.
Let me tell you my story. (See the video) 
I have to go to find 'HUGE MONSTER' to save my friends and villagers. 
All villagers except me were eaten by 'Huge Monster'... 
I'm supposed to be released for iPhone or iPad on Apple App Store.
Please wait for me!!  
I think you will help me out, even though my adventure is tough. 
Plz, help me.
